-- Hublot’s Biver Interested in Buying Le Temps, Tribune Says
-- B y   T h o m a s   M u l i e r
-- 2013-10-11T06:09:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-11/hublot-s-biver-interested-in-buying-le-temps-tribune-says.html
Hublot Chairman Jean-Claude Biver
says he wouldn’t buy the Swiss newspaper for money but rather
for patriotism for the French-speaking region of  Switzerland ,
Tribune de Geneve reports.
*Says newspaper ‘shouldn’t die nor wither’: Tribune
*NOTE: Ringier and Tamedia said in an Oct. 8 statement they want
to sell their stakes in Le Temps: Link to statement in French:
